ervice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/12/163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F12%2F163227_7529c4fae71b5dd7ff9beea275ef5ec9.jpg&h=ca5c499d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n根本係大陸仔打啲字<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n又唸又窩又奔，都唔知佢打乜柒！<br />\n你全家奔緊落地獄呀支那狗！！！！！<br />\n下世咪撚再落黎香港，生生世世做中蟈人呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n經過追擊之下，終於承認自己係支那狗，<br />\n並聲稱自己永遠都唔上LIHKG<br />\n又改名-你仲唔仆街<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/15/233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F15%2F233117_e7fca3f6eec812664dffae026e0b271d.jpg&h=443b5ea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n但好景不常，經過一個月潛水又俾我見返佢！<br />\n所以只好繼續我嘅追擊行動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n條柒頭份人極度陰險，之前開post叫雞俾人放飛機開post起人底！<br />\n<br />\n小心呢件ptgf<br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/77362/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n仲話叫ptgf唔係叫雞喎，你咪撚玩啦！<br />\n人地唔撚so你好出奇咩？<br />\n雞都嫌棄你賤種畜生呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n係咁多先，希望樓主真係好好守承諾，<br />\n唔好再上黎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>條賤種拎強姦慘劇黎講笑<br />\n聲稱要合法化強姦十點後外出嘅女人</strong></span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/237323/page/1?ref=ios</a><br />\n<br />\n你喺網上唔代表可以乜都講<br />\n你上得連登就代表你係一個人<br />\n唔該你地似返個人<br />\n認撚住條雞蟲份人係幾撚低劣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d172a7eb25f59d4af062ee7d6984b0eb0744170","tid":288672,"uid":36770,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T12:16:15.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>寂寞潮水 人痛心陰莖拔去</blockquote><br />\n我已不𢤦得哭笑 望著你 烏龜告退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"300ccb457474e8a4b12b7c3b17a94cdf5fd6353c","tid":288672,"uid":83813,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-18T13:00:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>寂寞潮水 人痛心陰莖拔去</blockquote><br />\n我已不𢤦得哭笑 望著你 烏龜告退<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大陸仔 屌你老母<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23aa5704812a869972bb1301ea99eead21016236","tid":288672,"uid":4301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T20:40:52.000Z","msg":"大陸仔 返天涯啦"},{"pid":"ffa8900a85a395bf482e88cce567380f88fdaa16","tid":288672,"uid":61281,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-19T21:03:53.000Z","msg":"原來當天的所愛是隻狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33fbe84f7ac673639240b63647251e17202b372f","tid":288672,"uid":17248,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-21T09:37:18.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>你覺得好有趣?<br />\n<br />\n咪搞尻呢啲歌啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n我好鍾意呢首歌架 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  咪撚尻改啦 都唔撚好笑 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.